'''昌迪加尔岩石花园'''（Rock Garden of Chandigarh）是[[印度|印度]][[昌迪加尔|昌迪加尔]]的一个雕塑花园，又名内克·钱德岩石花园（Nek Chand's Rock Garden），以其创始人、一位政府官员内克·钱德·赛尼命名，在1957年的业余时间秘密地开始修建。它完全由工业、家庭垃圾和废弃物品建造。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=3CdgUwZBNwIC&pg=PA321&dq=Rock+Garden,+Chandigarh&as_brr=0#PPA319,M1 Nek Chand Rock Garden] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3CdgUwZBNwIC&pg=PA321&dq=Rock+Garden,+Chandigarh&as_brr=0#PPA319,M1 |date=20200601082008 }} ''Sublime Spaces and Visionary Worlds: Built Environments of Vernacular Artists'', by Leslie Umberger, Erika Lee Doss, Ruth DeYoung Kohler, Lisa Stone. Published by Princeton Architectural Press, 2007. {{ISBN|1-56898-728-5}}. Page 319-Page 322.</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-01/chandigarh/32494297_1_night-tourism-feasibility-study-prominent-tourist-destinations |title=Night tourism to light up ‘rocks’ |newspaper=The Times of India |date=2012-07-01 |accessdate=2012-10-30 |archive-date=2013-01-26 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130126225232/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-01/chandigarh/32494297_1_night-tourism-feasibility-study-prominent-tourist-destinations |dead-url=yes }}</ref>直到18年后（1975年）才被当局发现。当时已经占地{{convert|12|acre|ha|adj=on}} <ref>{{cite web|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=B7T4T1oK_-IC&pg=PA126&dq=rock+garden+chandigarh&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EzbxT6rUGILrrQeXyPi9DQ&ved=0CDsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=rock%20garden%20chandigarh&f=false|title= Picturing South Asian Culture in English: Textual and Visual Representations|access-date= 2020-11-16|archive-date= 2020-05-31|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200531220740/https://books.google.com/books?id=B7T4T1oK_-IC&pg=PA126&dq=rock+garden+chandigarh&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EzbxT6rUGILrrQeXyPi9DQ&ved=0CDsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=rock%20garden%20chandigarh&f=false|dead-url= no}}</ref>。今天，它占地{{convert|40|acre|ha}}。

岩石花园位于苏赫纳湖附近。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/life-and-style/kids/article2081192.ece? |title=Working wealth out of waste |access-date=2020-11-16 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718203056/http://www.thehindu.com/life-and-style/kids/article2081192.ece |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 

该花园每天接待5，000多人，自成立以来，游客超过 1200 万人次<ref>{{cite web|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=gL7pGaL3vooC&pg=PA125&dq=rock+garden+chandigarh&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EzbxT6rUGILrrQeXyPi9DQ&ved=0CGcQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=rock%20garden%20chandigarh&f=false|title= Discover India by Rail|access-date= 2020-11-16|archive-date= 2020-06-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200601110327/https://books.google.com/books?id=gL7pGaL3vooC&pg=PA125&dq=rock+garden+chandigarh&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EzbxT6rUGILrrQeXyPi9DQ&ved=0CGcQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=rock%20garden%20chandigarh&f=false|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

